        -:  707:// Logic for distributing data into bins (Optimized to O(N))
        -:  708:static void compute_hist_logic(NV *restrict x, size_t n, NV *restrict breaks, size_t n_bins, 
        -:  709: size_t *restrict counts, NV *restrict mids, NV *restrict density) {
