        -:  975: *	  a,,c  -- never '' or "". A zero-length field cannot contain a
        -:  976: *	  separator, quote, or newline, so it never needs quoting.
        -:  977: *	- The separator is treated as a string (strstr), so multi-character
        -:  978: *	  separators work; an empty separator never triggers quoting.
